t","text":"The trick for Michael was to conjure for his son an illusory orderliness; only"},{"type":"text","text":"alone at night, when the boy was asleep, could Michael acknowledge the chaos"},{"type":"text","text":"he kept hidden from his son."},{"type":"text","text":"chimerical, fanciful, fictive, imaginary"},{"type":"entry","text":"palpable","headword":"palpable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.可触知的，可察觉的：明显的（tangible，perceptible,noticeable)"},{"type":"text","text":"['palpabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：palp（摸）+able→摸得到的→可触知的：明显的"},{"type":"entry","text":"defer","headword":"defer"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 遵从, 听从(to yield with courtesy) ;: 延期(to put off to a future time; delay)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'fs:r]"},{"type":"entry","text":"stasis","headword":"stasis"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.停滞(motionlessness)"},{"type":"text","text":"['steisIs]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：sta（看作stay）+sis发音同cease）→保持停止状态→停滞"}]},{"number":43,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"text","text":"suggest greater diversity today, while in actuality there has been either sfasis or"},{"type":"text","text":"decreased diversity."},{"type":"entry","text":"complacent","headword":"complacent"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.自满的，得意的（self-satisfied,smug)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam'plersnt]"},{"type":"text","text":"注意不要和complaisant（adj.随和的）相混"},{"type":"text","text":"图complacency（n.满足，安心）"},{"type":"entry","text":"perspicuous","headword":"perspicuous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.明晰的，明了的(clearly expressed or presented)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ps:r'sprkjuas]"},{"type":"entry","text":"seclusion","headword":"seclusion"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.隔离（the act of secluding):隔离地（a secluded or"},{"type":"text","text":"[s1’klu:3n]"},{"type":"text","text":"isolated place)"},{"type":"text","text":"图bein seclusion处于被隔离状态"},{"type":"text","text":"Mmiilz"},{"type":"entry","text":"uncompromising","headword":"uncompromising"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不