zit]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（加强）+quis（寻求）+ite→一定要找到的东西→必要的"},{"type":"text","text":"Biography is a literary genre whose primary requisite is an ability to"},{"type":"text","text":"reconstruct imaginatively the inner life of a subject on the basis of all the"},{"type":"text","text":"knowable external evidence."},{"type":"entry","text":"tendentious","headword":"tendentious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 有偏的(marked by a tendency in favor of a particular point of view)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ten'denfas]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：tend（倾向）+ent(存在）+ious→有倾向的→有偏见的"},{"type":"text","text":"tendentiousness (n. 偏见)"},{"type":"entry","text":"conjecture","headword":"conjecture"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.推测，胞测v猜想，推测"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'dzektfar]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：con（共同）+ject（扔）+ure（表行为）→大家一起扔（思想）→推测"},{"type":"text","text":"presume, suppose, surmise"},{"type":"text","text":"conjectural(adlj.凭猜测的；凭推测的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"ingenious","headword":"ingenious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.聪明的（clever)：善于创造发明的，心灵手巧的（original, inventive)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xn'dzinias]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（向内）+geni（看作gen，产生）+ous→有产生能力的→善于创造发明"},{"type":"text","text":"的：注意不要和ingenuous（adj.纯真的，纯朴的：坦率的）相混"},{"type":"entry","text":"proprietary","headword":"proprietary"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 私有的(privately owned and managed)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pra'prara,teri]"},{"type":"entry","text":"introspect","headword":"introspect"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 内智i(an examination of one’s own thoughts and feelings)"},{"type":"text","text":"[intra'spekt]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：intro（在内）+spect（看）→向内看→内省"},{"type":"text","text":"introspection（n.自省：反省）"},{"type":"entry","text":"calculated","headword":"calculated"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 精心策划的，蓄意的(carefully planned to get what you want)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kaelkjulertrd]"},{"type":"text","text":"deliberate, considered, reasoned"},{"type":"entry","text":"glaciation","headword":"glaciation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 冰JIIf作用(the process or result of land being covered by glaciers)"},{"type":"text","text":"[glerfi'erfn]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：glaci(冰）+ation→冰川l作用"},{"type":"text","text":"Geologic record contains no evidence for widespread glaciation until 2.3"},{"type":"text","text":"billion years ago."},{"type":"entry","text":"extirpate","headword":"extirpate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.消灭，根除(to remove or destroy completely)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ekstarpert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ex（向外）+(s)tirp（根）+ate→向外连根拔起→根除"},{"type":"text","text":"eliminate"},{"type":"entry","text":"cagey","headword":"cagey"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 守口如瓶的S(not wanting to give someone information)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kerd3i]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：cage（笼子）+y→把秘密关在笼子里→守口如瓶的"}]},{"number":45,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"relegation","headword":"relegation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 贬低(the fact of being given a lower or less important position, rank, etc. than"},{"type":"text","text":"[,relr'ger{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"before)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（相反）+leg（讲，读）+ation→讲反话→贬低"},{"type":"definition","text":"v强压怒火：生闷气(fume)"},{"type":"entry","text":"seethe","headword":"seethe"},{"type":"text","text":"[si:0]"},{"type":"text","text":"seetheover因某事而慎怒或不满"},{"type":"entry","text":"bedrock","headword":"bedrock"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.基本事实，基本原则(basis)：基岩（the solid rock that underies loose materia)"},{"type":"text","text":"['bedra:k]"},{"type":"text","text":"组合词：bed（河床）+rock（岩石）→河床上的岩石→基岩"},{"type":"entry","text":"ingenuity","headword":"ingenuity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 独创力(inventive skill or imagination; clevermess)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xndza'nu:ati]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自ingenious（adj有创造力的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"comportment","headword":"comportment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.行为; 举止; 表现(manner of behaving: bearing: deportment)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam'p>:rtmant]"},{"type":"text","text":"词根记亿：comport(举止）+ment→举止；行为"},{"type":"entry","text":"leaven","headword":"leaven"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 给-添趣(to make sth. more interesting by adding sth. to it)"},{"type":"text","text":"[levn]"},{"type":"entry","text":"marginalize","headword":"marginalize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v使边缘化，排挤(to relegate to an unimportant or powerless position)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ma:rdginalarz]"},{"type":"text","text":"过来自marginal （adj边缘的）"},{"type":"text","text":"marginalization (n. 边缘化)"},{"type":"entry","text":"cartographic","headword":"cartographic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 制图的(connected with the art or process of drawing or making maps)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:rta'grafrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自cartography（n.制图）"},{"type":"definition","text":"A divide between aesthetic and technical considerations has played a crucial"},{"type":"text","text":"role in mapmaking and cartographic scholarship."},{"type":"text","text":"cartographically (adv. 地图制图学地)"},{"type":"entry","text":"melancholy","headword":"melancholy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 忧郁(sadness or depression of the spirits)"},{"type":"text","text":"['melanka:li]"},{"type":"text","text":"dejection, depression, desolation, despondence, dolefulness, melancholy"},{"type":"entry","text":"deify","headword":"deify"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 神化,崇拜(to treat someone as a god)"},{"type":"text","text":"['derfar]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：dei（神明）+fy（--化)→神化"},{"type":"entry","text":"laudatory","headword":"laudatory"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 称赞的(of, relating to, or expressing praise)"},{"type":"text","text":"[lo:dato:ri]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自laud（n.赞美）"},{"type":"entry","text":"archipelago","headword":"archipelago"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 群岛， 列岛(a large group of islands)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:rkr'pelagau]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：archi（主要的）+pelago（海洋）→主海