（adj.表示钦佩的：赞美的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"torpor","headword":"torpor"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.死气沉沉(extreme sluggishness of function)"},{"type":"text","text":"['toirpar]"},{"type":"text","text":"dullness, languor, lassitude, lethargy"},{"type":"entry","text":"aberrant","headword":"aberrant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 越轨的 (turning away from what is right); 异第的(deviating from what is"},{"type":"text","text":"[ae'berant]"},{"type":"text","text":"normal)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ab（离开）+err偏离）+ant→偏离正轨→越轨的"},{"type":"text","text":"aberration (n. 越轨)"},{"type":"entry","text":"perforce","headword":"perforce"},{"type":"definition","text":"adv.必须：必定(by necessity)"},{"type":"text","text":"[par'fo:rs]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：per（凭借）+force（力量）→凭借这股力量必定成功→必定"},{"type":"entry","text":"credential","headword":"credential"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 证明书(something that gives a tile to credit or confidence) v 提供证明书"},{"type":"text","text":"[kra'den1]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：cred（相信）+ent+ial→使人信服的文件→证明书"},{"type":"entry","text":"foretell","headword":"foretell"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 预知, 预言 (to tell of or describe beforehand)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fo:r'tel]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：fore（预先）+tell（说）→预先说出来→预言"},{"type":"entry","text":"unfeeling","headword":"unfeeling"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 漠不关心的(not sympathetic to others);无情的(having no physical feeling or"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'fi:lrn]"},{"type":"text","text":"sensation)"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：un（没有）+feeling（感觉）→没有感觉的→无情的"},{"type":"text","text":"insentient, ruthless"},{"type":"entry","text":"compartmentalize","headword":"compartmentalize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.分开，划分（to divide it into separate sections)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam,pa:rt'mentalarz]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：com（表加强）+part（分开）+ment+al+ize（使·-）→分开"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.尊重：敬重（torespect）"},{"type":"entry","text":"esteem","headword":"esteem"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'sti:m]"},{"type":"entry","text":"pedigree","headword":"pedigree"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 家谱 (a list of ancestors; a family tree)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pedrgri:]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ped（脚）+i+gree（看作crane，鹤）→像鹤脚一样的树状图→家谱"}]},{"number":52,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 03 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"flabbergast","headword":"flabbergast"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使大吃—惊(to make a strong impression on with something unexpected)"},{"type":"text","text":"[flaebar,gaest]"},{"type":"entry","text":"bountiful","headword":"bountiful"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj大量的，巨大的（large)：慷概的（generous)"},{"type":"text","text":"[bauntrfl]"},{"type":"text","text":"ample, copious"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.单配偶，单配制，一夫—妻制（the state or custom ofhaving a sexual relationship"},{"type":"entry","text":"monogamy","headword":"monogamy"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma'na:gami]"},{"type":"text","text":"with only one partner)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：mono（单个）+gam（婚姻）+y→一夫一妻制"},{"type":"text","text":"monogamous （adj.单—配偶的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"objectionable","headword":"objectionable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj令人反感的(deserving disapproval; offensive)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ab'dzek{anabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈来自object（v反对）"},{"type":"entry","text":"superposition","headword":"superposition"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 叠加n(the placement of one thing above or on top of another)"},{"type":"text","text":"[su:parpa'zi{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：super（上）+pos（放置）+ition→在上面又放了一层→叠加"},{"type":"entry","text":"impermanence","headword":"impermanence"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 非永久性(the state of not lasting or staying the same forever)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xm'p3:rmanans]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：im（不，非）+per（贯穿，自始至终）+man（保持）+ence→不始终保持→"},{"type":"text","text":"非永久性"},{"type":"entry","text":"stupefaction","headword":"stupefaction"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 惊(great astonishment)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,stu:prfaek{n]