 connected argumentation, into isolated metaphors."},{"type":"entry","text":"lugubrious","headword":"lugubrious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 恶伤的(mournful, dismal, or gloomy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[la'gu:brias]"},{"type":"text","text":"gloomy"},{"type":"entry","text":"abandon","headword":"abandon"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 故弃(to stop believing in something); 停i上(to stop supporting or helping sb);"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'baendan]"},{"type":"text","text":"透弃，抛弃(to leave sb. with no intention of returning)"},{"type":"text","text":"国联想记忆：a+band（乐队）+on→乐队表演时抛开一切杂念→放弃"},{"type":"text","text":"abandon established principles 放弃既定的原则"},{"type":"text","text":"desert, relinquish"},{"type":"entry","text":"porcelain","headword":"porcelain"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.瓷，瓷器（china)"},{"type":"text","text":"['po:rsalin]"},{"type":"text","text":"Chinese porcelain 中国瓷器"},{"type":"text","text":"porcelaneous (aoji 瓷器的)"}]}]}